WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.101 --> 00:00:02.169
NO MATTER WHO BECOMES INDIA'S
NEXT PRIME MINISTER, THEIR

00:00:02.202 --> 00:00:04.671
ELECTION WILL HAVE GLOBAL
CONSEQUENCES.

